From 7b26bc97430561423b9daa733bf526af5aa87aff Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Z.ai Code" <z@container>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 15:15:10 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(api-keys): IP allowlist, rate limiting, audit log, edit
 & usage endpoints
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Round 2 security + management enhancements for the per-user API Keys system.
Ported from the sandbox demo and adapted to Supabase Auth + Postgres + the
existing i18n/UI patterns.

Schema (prisma/schema.prisma):
- ApiKey: add allowedIps (JSON array, default []), rateLimitPerMinute (Int?)
- New SettingsAuditLog model (create/update/revoke trail, with user+apiKey
  relations, indexed on [userId,createdAt] / [apiKeyId] / [action])

Library (src/lib/api-auth.ts):
- parseAllowedIps / serializeAllowedIps — JSON <-> string[] for the allowlist
- isIpAllowed — exact + CIDR match, IPv4 and IPv6 (BigInt-based, ES2017-safe)
- checkRateLimit — in-memory token bucket, persisted across hot reloads
- pruneRateBuckets — bounded memory cleanup
- rateLimitHeaders — X-RateLimit-Limit / -Remaining / Retry-After
- writeAuditLog + auditContext — best-effort audit persistence
- authenticateApiKey now enforces IP allowlist (403) + rate limit (429) and
  returns rateLimit info on both success and failure
- unauthorizedResponse attaches rate-limit headers automatically

Routes:
- POST /api/settings/api-keys — accepts allowedIps + rateLimitPerMinute, writes
  audit log
- PATCH /api/settings/api-keys/[id] — NEW: edit label/scopes/IPs/rate/expiry
  with before/after diff audit
- DELETE /api/settings/api-keys/[id] — now writes audit log
- GET /api/settings/api-keys/revoked — NEW: revoked keys + last-50 audit entries
- GET /api/settings/api-keys/usage — NEW: 7-day per-key + aggregate breakdown
- GET /api/public/v1/me — exposes allowedIps/rateLimitPerMinute + rate headers
- GET /api/public/v1/datasources — NEW (read scope)
- GET /api/public/v1/dashboards — NEW (read scope)
- POST /api/public/v1/queries — NEW (execute scope, SQL SELECT with auto-LIMIT)

UI (src/components/app/settings/api-keys/):
- dict.ts — add allowedIps/rateLimitPerMinute to ApiKeyView + CreatedApiKey,
  new UsageResponse/RevokedResponse/AuditLogEntry types, 40+ new i18n keys
  (en+es), isValidIpOrCidr client validator
- usage-chart.tsx — NEW: dependency-free SVG sparkline (7-day volume)
- create-api-key-dialog.tsx — IP allowlist tag input + rate-limit mode/value
- api-keys-manager.tsx — IP/rate badges, per-key sparkline, Edit dialog,
  collapsible Audit & revoked-keys panel
